Requirements:
python (tested with 2.4)
libiriverdb (tested with 1.6) -- get it from http://bodgitandscarper.co.uk/libiriverdb/
gtk with python bindings (tested with 2.8)
glade with python bindings (tested with 2.8)
ctypes (tested with 0.9.6) (NOTE: this is included with python 2.5)

Running:
Just run griver.py and you're good to go.
